RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT FIELD_NAME, FIELD_DESC FROM OLTMS_STATIC_FIELD_VALS WHERE FIELD_TYPE = 'ESC1' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O'

SELECT FIELD_VAL FROM CSTMS_UDF_VALS WHERE FUNCTION_ID = 'STDCIF' AND FIELD_NAME = 'TAXAUTHORITYID' AND REC_KEY IN (SELECT REC_KEY FROM CSTMS_UDF_VALS WHERE FUNCTION_ID = 'STDCIF' AND FIELD_NAME = 'VENDOR' AND FIELD_VAL = 'Y')
SELECT CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM OLTM_CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER_NO = (SELECT RTRIM(REC_KEY, '~') REC_KEY FROM CSTMS_UDF_VALS WHERE FUNCTION_ID = 'STDCIF' AND FIELD_NAME = 'TAXAUTHORITYID' AND FIELD_VAL = ?)

SELECT C.CONTRACT_REF_NO, C.CONTRACT_CCY FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT C WHERE C.CONTRACT_STATUS = 'A' AND C.AUTH_STATUS = 'A' AND C.MODULE_CODE IN ('OL', 'LP', 'LB') AND C.BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND C.PRODUCT_TYPE = 'L'ORDER BY C.CONTRACT_REF_NO
SELECT PROPERTY_CODE, PROPERTY_NAME FROM OLTM_PROPERTY_MASTER WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O'
